INSERT INTO `blog` (`id`, `blog_title`, `blog_category`, `image1`, `image2`, `description`, `description1`, `blog_url`, `tags`, `author_name`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 'Best Marketing Strategy For Digital Presence | Business Growth', 'Marketing', 'best-marketing-strategy-for-digital-presence.png', NULL, '<p><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Marketing strategy</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every business plan shall include the marketing strategy. If you aren&rsquo;t well prepared for the kind of people you are targeting as a client, then there is a huge chance that you will end up losing the majority of leads.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We all know that marketing and branding cannot happen overnight, a well-planned strategy is key to it. And the more time you invest in creating a well-researched full-fledged plan, the more you will build sales opportunities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>What is marketing strategy?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For achieving any goal, we need a plan. Thus, to market the product also, we need a proper blueprint to be implemented. Therefore, to proceed, we strategize things like target customers, price, the technique of marketing, etc. And this is called a marketing strategy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moreover, market strategy plays an essential role in your digital presence and business growth. Some strategies require more investment, implying extra time, resources, or effort to support them, while other strategies offer a greater reward and produce more valuable, long results than other efforts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The 4 P&rsquo;s</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A business plan that aims to attain a sustainable competitive advantage through digital marketing requires a strong and powerful strategy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In general, the marketing strategy is based on these four Ps:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Product</li>\r\n	<li>Price</li>\r\n	<li>Place&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Promotion</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let&#39;s now explore the marketing techniques for both B2B and B2C Marketing:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. <strong>Content Marketing:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Content Marketing is a type of marketing focused on creating, publishing, and distributing content for a targeted audience online. It attracts new customers by creating and sharing free but valuable content.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/content-writing/\">Content marketing helps in brand awareness</a> by portraying you as a thought leader in your domain digitally.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. <strong>Social Media Marketing&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Online presence over social media to connect with your audience and clients while creating your Brand Advocacy, increase sales, and drive enormous traffic for your website is a mandate these days.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The major social media platforms (at the moment) are Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, LinkedIn, Pinterest, YouTube, and Snapchat. There is also a range of social media management tools that help businesses get the most out of social media platforms. <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/social-media-marketing/\">Social media is the only platform that connects you with customers.</a> And to create brand awareness amongst them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>&nbsp;3. Storytelling:&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Storytelling is one of the most efficient ways of selling your product. Be it the media industry or YouTubers, or artists; everyone uses storytelling as their weapon to engage with their potential customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In a recent survey, almost 91% of the respondents reported having a positive emotional connection with at least one brand. Storytelling in marketing helps consumers understand why they should care about something, and it works to humanize your brand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>4. <strong>Search Engine Optimization:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/seo-optimization/\">Search engine optimization is a process of increasing visibility</a>, traffic, and awareness of a particular website using specific tools and preferred keywords.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With SEO, you can make sure that your website stands among the top on search engines with other top unpaid search results on Yahoo, Google, Bing, etc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Who does not want to top on Google Ranking? SEO is one of the most cost-effective ways to keep your brand competitive with similar companies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you know that almost 14% of customers on the website are due to SEO marketing, followed closely by 12% in social media marketing?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>5. Email Marketing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A highly effective way to nurture and generate leads until and unless your email does not get into a spam folder.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email marketing success is measured through open rates and click-through rates. Have you ever signed up for a newsletter on any blog or by any entrepreneur or a writer, maybe? It&#39;s just that.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You send commercial emails to the subscribers, making them aware of products, discounts on them, how the product is personalized for them.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The advantages of email marketing are price and ease. Compared to other types of marketing, emailing is an inexpensive way to advertise your company and its products or services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>6.&nbsp; Conversational Marketing</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A real-time interaction via a chatbot or live conversations that get the right information in front of prospects and customers at the right time allows them to self-service and get questions answered immediately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chatbots are artificially intelligent programs that can have a real-time conversation with the consumers on the sites. And not just that it can further be extended to social media programs, SMS&#39;s, emails, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have very well understood the techniques, so why not now look at how the magic of marketing strategy works on consumers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>The impact of marketing strategy</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>It helps to create awareness of the brand, which is eminent in today&rsquo;s time.</li>\r\n	<li>Then after the person is aware, it develops the interest of the customer to buy the product.</li>\r\n	<li>And finally, if the person feels satisfied with the marketing strategy, then he/she purchases the product or service.</li>\r\n	<li>But remember, your product or service should be as good as the marketing strategy because nowadays, customers tend to share their experiences on social media and spread word of mouth.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>So, these were the marketing strategies that help you to boost your sales.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Final judgement</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Although there are many other ways by which you can generate thousands of organic or inorganic traffic but the above six mentioned in both the B2B and B2C categories outsmarts all of them.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Along with a strong strategy, consistency, perseverance, and belief in your product will give the best result. And sooner there will be a large increase in sales and your organization will achieve a suitable advantage over other companies.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hence, give your best in developing an appropriate strategy, and you&rsquo;ll reap the benefits late on. Also, don&rsquo;t forget to take any assistance from us as we are always here to help you, guide you, and support you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>', 'Every business plan shall include the marketing strategy, market strategy plays an essential role in your business growth.', 'marketing-strategy', 'Marketing,Digital Marketing', 'Mona', '2021-07-28 15:47:27', '2021-08-10 12:44:10'),
(2, 'What is website designing | Why website designing play an important role', 'Website', 'what-is-website-designing-why-website-designing-play-an-important-role.png', NULL, '<p><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Website Designing Matters</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Indeed, everyone wants to look best in front of others. And to make yourself presentable, you do a lot of things which we don&rsquo;t need to mention. But what about your website? Don&rsquo;t you think that your website must look presentable too? Unquestionably, the answer is yes. So, why not we move ahead to understand what is website designing and why that is significant for a company? And the most important, how to design a website?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>What is website designing?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let&rsquo;s not go by the definition and only consider the facts to figure out what it means when people say to design a website?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To design a website does not mean that you have to sit with a pencil and paper to draw a layout. It simply means that you have to manage and construct your website in a way that is easy to handle and enhances the user experience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moreover, many factors are there while designing a site that we&rsquo;ll discuss later on, but first, let&rsquo;s understand its importance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Why website designing play an important role?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To understand this better, think of 2 websites. One of the websites is accurately aligned, maintained and you can easily access all the data without any hassle. On the other hand, when you visit the 2nd website, you see no coordination between the pages, no proper layout, and you find yourself stuck somewhere. As a result, you leave that site.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>From this, you can very well relate that website designing is a significant factor. Indeed, there&rsquo;s magic in website designing. So, for whom are we waiting? Let&rsquo;s discuss the things that matter while designing a website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>The things that matter</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Font and color</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It may seem like a small thing, but mind you, it is essential for a website. The font and color affect the psychology of a person. And not only this, but it also helps to convey our message to the users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For example, white color denotes peace, bold letters define the importance of anything said, some fonts and colors are considered informal, and others not. And that is how the science of fonts and colors work. So, keep in mind to choose the right font for your website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Layout</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just like values are the foundation of being a human being. Similarly, the layout is eminent for a website. It is an outline of the site. It is the most prominent element for designing a website as it is the face of the website. Hence, make sure to select your layout that is appealing and comfortable for the visitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Images and videos</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>How can anything look cool without images and videos? So, don&rsquo;t think before adding them. Just add them to have some aesthetic feels. And yes, it is also a significant factor to be considered. Furthermore, make sure that they have alt attributes to improve the ranking of a website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Speed</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the story, slow and steady wins the race. But this is not a story so, speed matters a lot. Otherwise, the users will leave the site, and you&rsquo;ll feel sorry forever. Thus, make sure the loading time is minimum. For this, conduct a speed audit and improve your site speed accordingly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Mobile friendly</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We need not tell you the importance of mobile phones nowadays. Most of the users access a website through a mobile phone or tabs. So, it is a mandated thing that your site should be made compatible with all the devices.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The magic of designing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you remember we were talking about the magic of designing? Hence, now it&rsquo;s the time to see the magic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Helps in marketing the website</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Marketing is a tough job, we all know. But what if your website design helps you market your site and brand within clicks? Yes, that is possible with the perfectly designed website. And a perfectly designed website will take care of all the above elements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Enhancing user experience</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Undoubtedly, the user must find the website easy to handle without any hassle. And if the user approves it, then think that you have conquered the world. Hence, ensure that the layout, fonts, colors, images are appropriate because it is worthy in the last.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>The site ranking&nbsp;</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When the users would visit and revisit the website, then obviously, site ranking improves. And it also results in driving more traffic to the website. Thus, validate everything before publishing the site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Forgot something?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We talked about everything from elements, significance to the magic of designing but forgot to talk about how to construct a website. Not to worry, here are the quick steps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Steps to design a website</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>After purchasing the domain and the hosting, log in to WordPress from c-panel.</li>\r\n	<li>Use any website builder like Elementor-Pro to customize the site.</li>\r\n	<li>Select the perfect template for the website or design your template.</li>\r\n	<li>Make changes in color, fonts, images, menu, and other required things.</li>\r\n	<li>Make the website mobile-friendly.</li>\r\n	<li>Add SEO proved content and images, videos to the site.</li>\r\n	<li>Publish your website.</li>\r\n	<li>And yes, don&rsquo;t forget to add relevant social media keys to your website.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bonus tip</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, we have a bonus tip for you all, and that is to make your logo first. It will not only help you to build the website effectively but will also build a positive image in front of the users.&nbsp;Moreover, you&rsquo;ll find ease while selecting colors for your website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Final words</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Interestingly, the only way to increase the reach and engage with your users in this internet era is to have a website and <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/social-media-marketing/\">social media presence.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>And for that, it is again significant to design your website in a presentable manner with proper font, alignment, content, SEO, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>And now you have successfully understood how to design your website. So, the internet is all yours. Start working on your website straight away by taking into account all the elements and factors. See what you can do to design the site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>And we know you know that we are here for any assistance or support. So, knock on our doors anytime, and we will be happy to assist you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>', 'now we will se what is website designing and why that is significant for a company everyone wants to look best in front of others', 'website-designing', 'Website,Website Designing,Web Development', 'Mona', '2021-07-28 15:55:18', '2021-08-10 13:10:22'),
(3, 'Affiliate Marketing Future | How to Boost Your Growth', 'Affiliate Marketing', 'affiliate-marketing-future-how-to-boost-your-growth.png', NULL, '<p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Affiliate marketing could be an overall strategy to drive deals and produce substantial online income. According to research, affiliate marketing is anticipated to reach $6.8 billion in 2020, and by 2022 it is expected to touch $8.2 billion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sound Internetising, no?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amazingly beneficial to both brands and partner marketers, the new thrust towards less conventional affiliate marketers, this whole thing can be an overall strategy to drive deals and produce substantial online income.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Although, there&#39;s one question that everybody needs an answer to What is the long-term future for Affiliate marketing&nbsp;<strong>work from home</strong>?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let&#39;s find it out!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>What is affiliate marketing, and how it works?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Affiliate marketing is an online deals strategy that lets a product proprietor increment sales by permitting others focusing on the same audience&mdash;&quot;affiliates&quot;&mdash;to gain a commission by prescribing the products to others.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Simultaneously, it makes it conceivable for associates to win cash on item deals without making items of their own.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Affiliate marketing includes alluding to an item or benefit by sharing it on a web journal, social media stages, or site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To take part in Affiliate marketing, you&#39;ll have to take these straightforward steps, and you&#39;ll get your answer on&nbsp;<strong>how to make money online:</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Find and connect with an Affiliate marketing program&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Choose which offers to promote&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Obtain an exciting Affiliate link to connect</li>\r\n	<li>Share those links on your web blog, social media stages, or website&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Collect a commission anytime&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>How do I become an affiliate marketer?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. <strong>Select a Niche</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>First, the step of your training to how to become an affiliate marketer includes finding out which associate items to offer and sell. This is the step to target the audience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Research Programs&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>After you&#39;ve picked a specialty, the next step is to discover which program out there can help you promote products in your thing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is a fundamental checklist that you should contemplate before you progress with a particular program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>What retailers are utilizing the affiliate program you&#39;re looking at?</li>\r\n	<li>How much percentage are you likely to obtain from your plan?</li>\r\n	<li>Do you want to be connected with the business and the embers selling through it?</li>\r\n	<li>What kind of assistance does the business present you with?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Build Your Platform&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The first two steps were centered on making a difference in your investigation. From here on out, you&#39;ll begin creating the stage that makes a difference in the success path to becoming an affiliate marketer. The two most well-known ways that affiliate marketer work includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/website-designing/\">Creating websites like blogs</a> or marketplaces.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Running paid ads with <strong>Adwords&nbsp;</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Create and Distribute Top-Notch Content&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Creating content is one of the ultimate steps of your pre-affiliate travel. In that way, it&#39;s moreover the door to the beginning of your associate showcasing endeavors. It doesn&#39;t matter if you&#39;re blogging or distributing advertisements; when you&#39;ve hit this stage, you&#39;re within the domestic extend of learning how to be an affiliate marketer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How much money do affiliate marketers make?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Low-level affiliates, who gain up to $300/day</li>\r\n	<li>Intermediate affiliates, who win from $300/day up to $3,000/day</li>\r\n	<li>High-level affiliates, who win over $3,000/day</li>\r\n	<li>Super affiliates or, as you&#39;ll be able to regularly discover them, being called, &quot;gurus of member marketing,&quot; who make more than $10,000/day.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What are the advantages of affiliate marketing?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Affiliate marketing is performance-based&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>It helps broaden your audience&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Affiliates can boost your reputation&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>It&#39;s cost-effective&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Affiliates can quickly scale your activity (and sales)&nbsp; with <strong>Clickbank</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Why affiliate marketing is the future?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The affiliate marketing industry has, over a long time, experienced various changes that have dynamically influenced the key players. Notwithstanding the changes, it has been seen as a foundation of online commerce through the adequacy of blog-based and PPC substance promoting. The long run of affiliate marketing has raised a very blend with advert players predicting different patterns. As much because it may be troublesome for anybody to tell long-term accurately, a few advancements ought to be self-evident.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Does affiliate marketing still work in 2021?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Future of Affiliate marketing is quite evident, and these trends tell us that it is going to touch the sky in the year 2021 as well:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1. Online coupon Sites&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>2. SMS-centered Pay Per Call&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>3. Visual Marketing&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>4. QR-Code Campaigns&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>5. Greater Networks&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>6. Boosted Brand Globalization&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>7. Data-Based Targeting&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Boundless Growth</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Affiliate marketing for beginners&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are a beginner that is going down this lane, then you need to know terms like:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pay-Per-Click (</strong><strong>PPC</strong><strong>):</strong> The partner gets paid for all clicks created, notwithstanding whether a lead or deal happened. It is typically decently uncommon since all the hazard is on the item creator.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pay-Per-Lead (PPL):</strong> The affiliate gets paid for each lead they created. This can be an internet frame accommodation, trial creation, or any pre-purchase. This is often a shared chance on both the dealer and the affiliate.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pay-Per-Sale (PPS): </strong>The associate gets paid for each deal they created. This is often the major standard demonstration since all the chance is on the member.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>', 'Affiliate marketing is an online deals strategy, According to research, affiliate marketing is anticipated to reach $6.8 billion in 2020', 'affiliate-marketing', 'Affiliate Marketing,Affiliate Marketing Future', 'Mona', '2021-07-28 15:57:45', '2021-07-28 16:14:08'),
(4, 'Online Promotion Proven Steps | Do Low Cost Online Brand Promotion', 'Promotion', 'online-promotion-proven-steps-do-low-cost-online-brand-promotion.png', NULL, '<p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Online Promotion have come a long way since the dawn of marketing. From traditional methods to new-age technology-driven systems, the transitional growth and prospects for significant market creation, targeting, and retention have multiplied exponentially. As an intelligent marketing manager, we understand that it is your top priority to balance your digital marketing targets vis-&agrave;-vis your marketing budget and core competencies. This is where our role as a top-grade digital marketing agency comes in.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>What we can do for your business</strong> for online promotion</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In literal terms, a digital marketing agency engages in online marketing tactics and promotion strategies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a multi-dimensional full-service agency whose focus is to target your ideal customers. Get their attention, and sustain a strong relationship with them. This is skillfully propagated with the aid of versatile channels and market-driven strategies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>From minor to the well-set, it is not rare for businesses to handle their online presence and growth by themselves. The imperative to function within a marketing budget is another reason why many firms shy away from online marketing agencies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In good practicality, as an <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/\">online marketing company</a>, we are quite the help to your marketing plan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let us understand this better by looking into the promotional features we offer as a full-service digital marketing company: -</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:group --><!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} --></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Content Marketing</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Email Marketing</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Online Advertising (PPC)</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Social Media Marketing</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- /wp:group --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>No &lsquo;one mix fixes<em>&nbsp;all&rsquo;</em>&nbsp;regarding an excellent online promotion campaign. The market is distinctly dynamic and requires a highly flexible combination of strategies, tactics, and online systems regularly updated. It is not productive for any business, big or small, to focus their attention solely on keeping up with this ever-changing online environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We not only formulate the ideal digital promotion campaign for you. We take it one step further with methodical and foolproof execution of the best digital marketing practices suitable to your needs while keeping up with unforeseen developments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Why choose us as your digital marketing agency?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are masters of online marketing. When you choose us, you can rest assured that you will get the perfect promotion mix for your business. From an expert analysis of the latest market trends to the appropriate marketing tools and best practices, we will deliver all the goods essential for your success online.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is a list of the key functions you can expect from us: -</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. <strong>Expansion of your brand&rsquo;s reach</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Online promotion is the baseline for our core competencies as an online marketing company. Expansion of your brand&rsquo;s reach in the digital realm entails the application of polished online promotion strategies that meet and maintain customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your brand is promised a high-level reach through the following: -</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Increased website visibility achieved through buyer persona development</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Application of call-to-action keywords researched after an in-depth analysis of how your customers can reach you</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Social media marketing techniques to increase your reach through social media platforms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. <strong>Growth of organic traffic on your website</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The success of your campaign depends on the extent of the organic traffic generated on your website. You know this, and so do we. Generation of organic traffic requires a detailed understanding of the search algorithms of search engines, differences in customer journeys, and inbound marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With us by your side, an increase in your organic traffic, i.e., prospective customers who land on your website through search engine research, is confirmed. This is a cost-effective benefit for you. You will now be interacting with a more significant number of quality leads who pose a higher probability of becoming confirmed customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3. <strong>Sales-centric lead generation</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As your agency, we are well-versed with your sales funnel, your marketing objectives, and the in-and-out of your business. We will use this information and our existing expertise to create the perfect mix of social media marketing, search engine optimization, content marketing, and similar inbound marketing promotional methods. This ensures that your leads are directed from the top to the bottom of your sales funnel through better conversions and sales.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your customers are out there. It is simply a matter of precision.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><em>You have to reach the right people at the right time, with the right message delivered through the suitable medium.</em></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>And we know how that is done.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>4. <strong>Extension of your marketing mix</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We function as a thoroughly specialized yet cost-effective extension of your in-house marketing department. As a partner in your digital marketing campaign, we strive to implement our knowledge and methodologies to further your marketing goals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We value your insights and add our own to build a framework of savvy Inbound marketing strategies that align with creating sales-oriented leads. With us, you will have a team of dedicated professionals who want to offer you the best of what a great digital promotions plan can unfold for your business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>', 'Online promotion is the baseline for our core competencies as an online marketing company. As your agency, we are well-versed with your sales', 'online-promotion', 'Promotion,Online Promotion', 'Mona', '2021-07-28 16:43:08', '2021-07-28 16:43:08'),
(5, 'Content Writing Strategies | Tips For Effective Content Writing', 'Content Writing', 'content-writing-strategies-tips-for-effective-content-writing.png', NULL, '<p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Content writing is the transfer of specific information to digital media. Content writers are the ones who design the concept of the content. You must draw the content well to seize the audience and make them read the entire blog.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>What can you do to make your content compelling?&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Do a Research:&nbsp;</strong>Conduct good research on the topic before writing content. Good research prepares you for writing and packs you with related information and ideas.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Frame a Magnetic Headline:&nbsp;</strong>Make an eye-catching headline that the reader will find attractive. Your headline should be capable of arousing curiosity in the reader, and headlines are the advertisements of your content.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design an Interesting Lead:</strong>&nbsp;It is essential to make the first sentences impressive. They must grab the attention of the reader, insisting them to read further.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Impress with Accuracy:&nbsp;</strong>The information you pass on to your audience must be accurate and free of exaggerations and hype. Your content must be believable, or else it can question your credibility.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content Perfection: </strong>The initial sentences of your content should answer all the &#39;why questions: why, what, when who, and where. The lack of this information will not be appealing to the audience, and your content may seem imperfect.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Insert Quotes:</strong>&nbsp;Quotations will help the audience and write a citation for the quotation. It can also grab their attention.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Focus on your Message:&nbsp;</strong>Identify your content&#39;s purpose and the message that you want to convey to the readers. It can organize your content and ensure easy reading for the readers. You can avoid ambiguities and confusion at the initial stage by structuring your content.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stand Odd in Uniqueness:&nbsp;</strong>Determine your content&#39;s goal and present it in a unique manner that makes your content stand different from others. Your writing tone must grab the attention of your target audience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Use Active Voice:</strong>&nbsp;Always use active voice because it focuses on the action. The focal point might change if the sentence is written in a passive voice and may bore the readers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Conversation can be Good: </strong>Interact with your readers to grab their attention. Implementing a conversational tone in your blog makes it interesting. Also, never forget to add questions that boil the curiosity in the readers. A blend of quotations, questions, information, and images can enhance your blog.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chop your Sentences:</strong>&nbsp;It is essential to limit the length of your sentence. Therefore, cut your sentences but never slip off your ideas. Your content must be with important and complex ideas in simple sentences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content Optimization:&nbsp;</strong>You should optimize digital content with short paragraphs. Employ these techniques to make your reader read the whole blog.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Assurance:&nbsp;</strong>Ensure that the information you have provided is accurate and check for grammar mistakes, spelling mistakes, and vocabulary. Imperfections can resist your audience from reading further.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Polish your Work:&nbsp;</strong>Edits are necessary to make your work perfect. Even experienced writers edit their careers to ensure the quality of their work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Do not Self-edit:&nbsp;</strong>Do not edit your content yourself as you are preoccupied with the content&#39;s ideas. Make somebody else read your content and point out the flaws in it.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>SEO FRIENDLY CONTENT WRITING</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Good use of keywords:</strong>&nbsp;Make your content rich in keywords but bombarding with keywords can tire your reader. Tag specific keywords if your blog supports tagging.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content Structure:</strong>&nbsp;Build your content with short paragraphs and employ specific fonts and types for your content and headline throughout the blog. A well-structured blog can make the audience read as they don&#39;t feel burdened with information.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Add Images:</strong>&nbsp;It is of no doubt that images can add beauty to your content. Select the most beautiful and unique photos to attract the audience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Share It:</strong>&nbsp;Make use of your social media accounts like Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram because they can increase your audience. Share your blog through social media and let them reach a large audience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Google Authorship:&nbsp;</strong>You can obtain Google authorship if you are in hold of a Google+ account. It can increase the readership of your content through personal promotion.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Natural Link Building:</strong>&nbsp;It is a rank factor for SEO. Linking to your article provides security if other websites take it.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Check if Everything Works Well: </strong>Google Analytics can help to track information related to your website. It lets you know the time spent by a viewer on the website and the page&#39;s views. You may then restructure your content based on the result. Link to other pages, too, as it can increase the page views.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>', 'Content writing is the transfer of specific information to digital media. Content writers are the ones who design the concept of the content.', 'content-writing', 'Content Writing,Content Writing Tips', 'Mona', '2021-07-28 16:48:20', '2021-07-28 16:48:20');
INSERT INTO `blog` (`id`, `blog_title`, `blog_category`, `image1`, `image2`, `description`, `description1`, `blog_url`, `tags`, `author_name`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(6, 'What is brand identity | Create a Powerful Brand Identity', 'Branding', 'brand-identity.jpeg', NULL, '<p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Brand Identity</strong> Have you ever observed fruits? If not, then you must look at them now. Just think about it. What would have happened if mango&rsquo;s name would be apple and apple&rsquo;s name would be orange. Do not seem correct? Right? That is the reason why identity is so important.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can take the example of anything in the world &amp; you&rsquo;ll see that identity matters a lot. Without having any identity, everything seems to be meaningless. Think of the moment when a baby is born or the moment where individuals enter into a new relationship. Everyone and everything has a unique name and unique identity. Then what is brand identity?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Without wasting much time, we shall proceed to look at what brand identity is all about? And why is it so important?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What is <strong>Brand Identity</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let us not go on the technical part and understand brand identity as a layman. Brand identity is the impression of a brand created in the minds of customers. Various elements like logo, design, and tagline, helps in forming the image of a brand. It reflects features, story, aesthetics, promises, quality, and whatnot. That is why it is also an important aspect.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today, when we hear the line &ldquo;Taste the Thunder,&rdquo; we can very well relate it to thumbs up and can associate a tick mark with the Nike brand. It has become possible because these brands have built their brand identity. They have set a particular image about themselves that tells people about them, their brand, their product, etc. And here we get another reason that brand identity is eminent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Is it a significant aspect for a company?&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>What do you think, creating a brand identity is significant? Or is it just a name?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, you are thinking right undeniably, your brand identity is substantial. It is the face of the brand and makes you instantaneously noticeable to the people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Above and beyond, it creates a sense of trust and reliability that adds an advantage while building a customer base. Moreover, it not only assists you to retain old customers but also helps to attract new ones. And we are sure that nobody wants to lose this kind of opportunity. So, keeping in mind that time is money, why not find how to build a brand identity?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Building your Brand Identity</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Creating a brand identity package includes a few of the following elements:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Name</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shakespeare once said what&rsquo;s in name, but the reality is everything starts with the name. Thus, the brand name is the utmost important thing to decide. We hope you choose it carefully. Otherwise, you&rsquo;ll face penalties later on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The vision and mission</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is the next most important thing to decide. Your corporate identity depends upon the vision and mission of your company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The logo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong>There&rsquo;s a famous line that the soundest logos tell simple stories. Subsequently, it&rsquo;s time to pay focus on the logo. Also, do consider the color, size, shape, and design as all the factors count.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Website</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have a website, then focus on the color combinations used in your logo. Design your website with accurate alignment, typography, fonts, logo, and keeping in mind all the other aspects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The role of emotion</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Emotion plays a vital role as it helps you to connect with people. Nowadays, you may see brands using emotions as a part of their advertising campaign. There&rsquo;s a reason for this. It is done to connect with the audience and is very important also. Until the audience wouldn&rsquo;t connect, they&rsquo;ll not get attached to the brand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Don&rsquo;ts</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before deciding what to do, how to build a brand identity, remember some of the don&rsquo;ts, and you&rsquo;ll thank us later.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Think and act</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Think twice before you act. The wrong decision might have a bad influence on the future of your brand. Hence, think and take decisions wisely.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Be unique, and don&rsquo;t copy</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t copy your competitors because it will ruin your reputation some or the other day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Be constant&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to build trust, then follow consistency, and you&rsquo;ll surely win sooner or later.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The decision</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Creating a personal or corporate brand identity is not an easy task. It requires a lot of time and consistency. But, if you do it well, then you may reap its benefits over a long period.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also, always focus on creating a brand identity that emotionally connects your brand with people and is different from your competitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you wish to stand out from the crowd, then you must consider brand identity seriously. It will not only create a positive image of your brand but will also help to raise your profits in the future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more advice, feel free to knock on the doors of <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/\" target=\"_blank\">idotcommers</a> to find solutions to all your branding problems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>', 'Without having any identity, everything seems to be meaningless. creating a brand identity is significant? Or is it just a name?', 'brand-identity', 'Branding,Brand Identity', 'Mona', '2021-07-28 16:51:21', '2021-07-28 16:51:21'),
(7, 'Why Website Audit Is Important | How To Do SEO Audit Of Website', 'Website', 'why-website-audit-is-important-how-to-do-an-seo-audit.png', NULL, '<p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The best way to understand a <strong>website audit </strong>is by paying a quick visit to our childhood days. Let us recall the age when we had Parent-teacher meetings, and we use to get report cards. Though that was tough, that was also necessary to have a reality check. There used to be an assessment, done to know what we have learned, what has been our performance. It was a check for us to identify our weak areas and to improve our performance next time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now, what do you think? Were those assessments worthy or not? Naturally, they were, as until and unless we find out the problem, how can we be expected to find the solution? Right?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The website audit is also similar in many aspects. So, let us examine what is web audit and what are its key factors?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Website Audit</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Everybody must have heard about swot analysis of a company. For those who have not heard, it is the analysis done by any company to find about its strength, weakness, opportunities, and of course, threats. It is a way to get an overview of the company&#39;s performance and to ascertain the scope of improvements.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Similarly, a website audit is a complete check-up of the website to analyze all the factors that may affect the site&#39;s performance. It tells us about the present scenario of the site and the improvements if to be made. Be it keywords or website speed, all of the aspects come under an audit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thus, we are now aware, what is a website audit. How about having a look at some of the main elements of a website audit?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Keywords</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You surf the net, and you get the result. But have you ever thought one website is on 1st and the other is on 4th? Why is this discrimination?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>No, that is just page ranking according to the keywords used in the website. So, keywords play a significant role in website performance. Therefore, generally, people use google keyword planner or other tools to find the keyword suitable for their website or a blog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Links</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are links provided to you on most of the sites. Those are there to create backlinks of the website that helps to improve the website ranking. Why? Because backlinks act as an authority for the site. Thus, the more backlinks, the more it will help to improve ranking. Main elements of a website audit?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mobile compatibility</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nowadays, to run a website, the website must be mobile-friendly. It means that a website should also be accessible appropriately from mobile phones. It helps the users to open the site wherever they want, which helps to improve the performance of the site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Speed check</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>What happens when a website takes time to load? We tend to leave that site and move to another one. Therefore, speed is a prominent factor in enhancing user experience. If the loading time would be faster, then it will help to boost website performance. So, make sure your website loading time is speedy, and if not, then check for the reasons that can lead to this like, sizeable data, unoptimized images, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sitemaps</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sitemaps are eminent for a website. Like your roll number helps your teacher to know that you have taken admission. Likewise, sitemaps help search engines to crawl and index a website. Thus, it improves website performance. For this, you can use free tools like seositechecker.com to check sitemap for your site. And you can also generate sitemaps using sitemap generators.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Content</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/content-writing/\">Content is as influential for a site </a>as we need to breathe. But, like poor quality of air can affect us. Similarly, poor content has the power to damage the site. So, if you want that your site works well, then focus on the content. It should be relevant, SEO proved, engaging, and undeniably informative for the users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>website Security</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your website should be secure. Yes, if your site is not safe, then nobody will visit your site. So, make sure you have HTTPS protocol. It will not only act as a safety for its users, but it will also help in improving the site compatibility.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>plagiarism</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t be a copycat; we must have heard this before. And this is the same for now also. If you would copy the content of others, then you&#39;ll not be able to survive in the internet era. Moreover, it may lead you back to square one because your search ranking would be highly affected by all this. So, the choice is yours if you want to copy others or be original. At last, you have to pay for all.<br />\r\nWe all can do these measures, but have you ever thought, why are we doing this? Therefore, now let us proceed to know the reason behind the SEO audit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Why SEO audit?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>To drive traffic to the website.</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Driving traffic to a website is the most vital aspect without which a website is not considered complete. As a consequence, a worthy website is a mandate to drive traffic. And website becomes worthy when the results of the SEO audit are good to go.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>To enhance google search ranking.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Site ranking and site traffic are connected. When the site can drive traffic, then automatically, it will enhance the google search ranking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Getting started</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every day before going somewhere, we look in the mirror to check that we are ready to leave. And that is what you have to do for your website every time you make changes to it. You have to take care of every factor, be it a keyword or any image. You have to make sure that your site is doing well. And for that, you must conduct an SEO audit regularly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You need not worry it is not tough at all. You only need the right tools and guidance. You can use tools like SEMrush for the free site audit. And of course, you can ask us anytime for any help and support.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>So, make sure you are perfectly ready before launching anything on your site, and for any assistance, you can knock on the doors of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/\">idotcommers</a>&nbsp;site anytime.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>', 'website audit is a complete check-up of the website to analyze all the factors that may affect the site\'s performance.', 'website-audit', 'Website Audit,SEO Audit', 'Mona', '2021-07-28 16:58:04', '2021-07-28 16:58:04'),
(8, 'Social Media Marketing | Best Ideas And Bonus Tips', 'Social Media', 'social-media-marketing-best-ideas-and-bonus-tips.png', NULL, '<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><strong>Social Media Marketing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Sky is the limit,&quot; We must have heard this over and over again in our life. Wait, you must be thinking, why are we saying this to you? Because that is what social media is doing, connecting the dots.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Be it a common man or a politician, the whole world is on social media. It is not only a platform but a virtual space where we meet new people, connect and share our beliefs and perspectives with the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Until social media arrived, no one has ever thought that there would be a time where we could connect with each being miles away.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>So straight away, we should continue to find out what social media marketing exactly is and why the content should be relevant to promote a product or a service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>What is Social Media Marketing?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Without getting involved in technical jargon, why not we directly try understanding the meaning of social media marketing in simpler terms.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We all are on social media platforms like Facebook, Pinterest, Twitter, Instagram, YouTube, etc. And we also see advertisements and what we call videos of influencers promoting a product without any fail. Henceforth, social media marketing means using the social platforms wisely to endorse a target product or a service.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Previously, there used to be advertisements and hoardings all around because that was the way back then. But now, we see content in the form of videos, graphics, blogs, and much more because that is the current trend.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the present era, social media is the only place where all your marketing can be done in half a shake without any Hussle, like magic. Thus, now we know social media marketing is an important aspect.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Relevance of The Content</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>What do you feel? Can you post anything on social media to promote your product? The answer to this is no. No, you cannot do this because proper strategizing is needed before posting anything. Just remember that you cannot post whatever you want. You have to post what people want to see and what is more valuable for them.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your content which you are creating must be relevant to the audience, must be <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/seo-optimization/\">SEO-proven</a>, and must be able to deliver your message to the audience. Otherwise, your product will not sell. Keep in mind the more relevant the content is, the more is the sale because the content is the king.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moreover, if you will use social media wisely, then only you&#39;ll get results in the long run.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Using Social Media Wisely</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Using social media wisely to market your product is not rocket science but, it is also not a piece of cake. So, you need to be a little careful while using social media. And for reference, you can keep following things in mind.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Identifying the target audience</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Horlicks for women is meant only for women and not everyone else. Thus, knowing your target audience is a mandate. You cannot sell everything to everybody. First, identify your target audience concerning your product and then proceed further.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Researching your competitors</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is eminent to keep a check on what competitors are doing. How well they are promoting their brand can also help you in the future. But take into account that you do not have to copy them. You have to be original to sustain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Decide the social media platform to promote your product.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are many social media platforms but, you cannot use all of them. Also, not every social platform is relevant for you. So, be clear in mind while deciding the social media platforms which you would be using.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Strategizing&nbsp;</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As mentioned already, strategy is significant. Hence, make sure you are pre-planning everything, Posts, content in posts, hashtags, platforms, SEO, image, and whatnot. And then implement your plan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Keep track of your activities as well.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You must also keep a check on your movements. Why? Because precaution is better than cure. One inappropriate content can ruin your image. And one right content can make your reputation in the world of social media.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now, without any delay, let us proceed further.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Using Social Media to Understand the Audience</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Drive traffic to the website</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You have to understand that audience is lazy, and they will never visit your site until it is exciting. Thus, it is a great way to drive traffic to your website. Provide links with every ad and where ever possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Creates an emotional connection with the audience</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is again necessary that your customers can relate themselves to your product. Always remember that product doesn&#39;t sell stories sell. So, try and connect with your audience for better results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Edge over the competitors</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Give your audience something that others aren&#39;t. You can&#39;t beat your competitors over prices every time and minute. So, think of new ideas to engage with them. Listen to their stories, share them, and if you can, then support them. Find your edge and work on it, and you&#39;ll find yourself in people&#39;s hearts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>The Bonus Tip</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>social media is the ultimate tool if you understand it. Identify the needs of your target audience, engage, and create a relationship with them. No other platform can give you this. So, make full use of this opportunity before it&#39;s too late.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Social Media Marketing: Good or Bad?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fascinatingly, nothing is good or bad, you need to use the opportunity wisely, and that is it. For social media marketing also, you need to be aware of how social media works, what type of content, advertisements are already there, and what is required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your brand will ultimately gain success, and also, it will earn a good number of profits once you understand the working of the internet community. It is vast so give it time, set your goals, and do proper research before starting.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just another piece of advice; consider it seriously, and we know you know that you can knock on our doors anytime for any query related to social media marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>', 'We all are on social media marketing platforms like Facebook, Pinterest, Twitter, Instagram, YouTube, etc. And we also see advertisements', 'social-media-marketing', 'Social Media,Social Media Marketing', 'Mona', '2021-07-28 17:01:51', '2021-07-29 13:21:02'),
(9, 'SEO Optimization How Search Engines work | Best SEO Practices', 'SEO', 'seo-optimization-how-search-engines-work.png', NULL, '<p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SEO Optimization </strong>The world was almost about to end&hellip; but <strong>SEO never stopped</strong>, and it will never stop from being online. With the world&rsquo;s biggest turmoil in history, look what all of us turned to when nothing was available and everything shut down as some zombie apocalypse had occurred; it felt like straight out of a movie scene. With the outer world getting destroyed, the internet world was being used x2 times the normal usage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many brands and companies were suffering a lot through the pandemic. Who would have thought that the 2008 recession wasn&rsquo;t the only thing that would create havoc around the entire world? People had a lot of free time now left on their own, so they started watching tv series, shopping for themselves, and stuff like that. But how to stand out from thousands of other such brands or websites that turn on our targeted audience&rsquo;s page? Well, the answer to that is SEO, and we provide that service to you so that you will always be on top and within your audience&rsquo;s vicinity (technically).&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Search that enables users to search for documents on the World Wide Web. A search engine aims to extract requested information from the huge database of resources available on the internet. Search engines become an important day-to-day tool for finding the required information without knowing where exactly it is stored.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Types Of Search Engines And How Search Engines Work</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>1. Crawler Based Search Engines</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>All crawler-based search engines use a crawler or bot, or spider for crawling and indexing the new content to the search database. There are four basic steps that every crawler-based search engine follows before displaying any sites in the search results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>2. Human Powered Directories</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Human-powered directories also referred as open directory system depends on human-based activities for listings. The process of indexing is explained as below:<br />\r\nThe site owner submits a short description of the site to the directory and the category it is to be listed. The submitted site is then manually reviewed and added in the appropriate category or rejected for listing. Keywords entered in a search box will be matched with the description of the sites. This means the changes made to the content of web pages are not taken into consideration as it is only the description that matters.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>3. Hybrid Search Engines</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hybrid Search Engines use both crawler-based and manual indexing for listings the sites in search results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most of the crawler-based search engines like Google uses crawlers as a primary mechanism and manual screening as a secondary mechanism. When a site is being identified for spammy activities, manual review is required before including it again in the search results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>What is Organic SEO Optimization?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is a natural way of getting a top ranking in SERP (search engine result page) without paying any search engines for the placement. This is a more preferable and trustworthy method of securing a high rank on SERP.<br />\r\nBenefits of Organic Search Engine Optimization:<br />\r\n&bull; Usually, normal users click more on organically optimized sites.<br />\r\n&bull; Results are long-lasting on search engine result pages.<br />\r\n&bull; Organic results are more trustworthy than inorganic results.<br />\r\n&bull; Organic service is cheaper than inorganic services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>The ultimate goal of SEO</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let&rsquo;s break that description down a bit to get a better understanding:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Ranking in search results</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When a user enters a search request on Google, they are shown a list of results. The results at the top of the first page attract the most attention, so it is important to get into the top two or three positions for as many relevant searches as possible (keywords).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. High-quality visitors</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is sometimes thought that SEO is all about getting as much traffic to a website as possible, but it is important to get good quality traffic. For example, a fashion boutique in Mumbai will benefit from a website visitor looking for a fashion boutique in Delhi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Increased quantity of visitors</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once the right visitors come to your website, the more, the better.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Organic search</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A search engine results page is usually made up of both paid-for ads and organic listings, i.e., results that are not paid-for ads. SEO is concerned with organic listings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What is the importance of search for websites?&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/website-design/\">Websites can attract visitors</a> to the website through organic search but can also get visitors from other sources:<br />\r\n&bull; Links from other websites (referral traffic);<br />\r\n&bull; Social media;<br />\r\n&bull; Email marketing;<br />\r\n&bull; Paid ads;<br />\r\n&bull; Offline marketing;<br />\r\nThe ideal situation is to attract high-quality visitors to the website in as many different ways as possible, but organic search will almost always be an important source. For many websites, it is the primary source of traffic, while it is a significant source for others. If websites want to attract visitors through organic search or attract more, one needs SEO optimization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>', 'It is very important to do seo optimization. It is a natural way of getting a top ranking in Search Engine Result Page SERP', 'seo-optimization', 'SEO,Search Engine Optimization,Best SEO Practices', 'Mona', '2021-07-28 17:05:05', '2021-07-28 17:16:40'),
(10, '10 Tips to improve your page quality for SEO', 'SEO', '10-tips-to-improve-your-page-quality-for-seo-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>page quality for SEO</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Endless time spent on the website and its technical aspects to get it ranked on Google. To attract crawlers to get your page indexed as an SEO person you look at all aspects of optimizing it. Even though you are careful your bounce rate is still the same moreover increasing and people are just not able to stay on your page. If you can resonate with these problems then this post might just be the ultimate solution for you.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>We will discuss how your page could use some extra love and what can be done to make them high-quality pages.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>You may already have taken a class about SEO and its technical aspects or you may have just started learning about it. The thought of mastering the art of SEO is dreadful but it is not impossible.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>To realise the <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/what-is-seo/\">importance of SEO</a> it is first crucial to look at your website&rsquo;s optimisation. Search engine optimisation may seem like a mix of keywords put correctly but the SERPs look at the whole picture nowadays.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>On the Yoast SEO blog they have coined a great term called the &lsquo;Holistic SEO&rsquo; that talks about all important aspects to get your website the dream ranking. It is a good read.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>Let&rsquo;s talk about the quality of your page and how to determine it.</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Getting started blindly on the first page and optimising it for no reason does not make sense. It is better to take a look at the website as a whole first and determine which pages need improvement.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Use Google Analytics</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>With the use of this tool called Google Analytics, one can specifically point out which page is not performing up to the mark. It lets you monitor how your customers search you online and navigate throughout their page. Most importantly it lets you know how many people visited, stayed, and exited the website. If they did exit, which page they leave the website from.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Google Panda is not cute but strict</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>When a company owns a website that has a large amount of information to share. They are tempted to regulate the same content on different websites. Do not let this temptation overpower your SEO goals. When the same content is found on different pages it is a case of duplicate content. With the introduction of Google Panda update, Google is now capable of penalizing your website if it finds duplicate content. This will hamper your rankings drastically.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Catch the low-quality pages</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Low-quality pages occur in groups and not as a single page. Old .HTML pages ending with a trailing slash or any attachment pages with too many numbers. These links need to be found and removed from Google. This will shed more light towards the important pages which need attention on priority. One tool that comes in handy for these checks is the screaming frog. Once a website link is entered it will perform an audit on all your pages and with each URL you can locate these low-quality pages.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>How to improve site performance?</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Need for speed</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Google is working on its new ranking factor page experience that will roll out in May 2021. This page factor will prioritize fast loading websites with great user experience over websites that take more load time and are not engaging. Speed of your website is a crucial determiner for its ranking in the SERPs</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>UX is the new King</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Your SEO strategy should focus on user experience because search engines are working hard on providing its customers exactly what they want in their query. The best result of a search does not mean the best answer but the best experience. Even if your website is slow but has a better answer to a query, Google will consider that and post your answer over others. Define your website goal clearly, what do you want your visitors to do? Read your blogs, buy your stuff, then your website design should define this goal.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Accessible to all, on all mediums</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Your website should be perfectly compatible with all browsers and all devices either a computer or a mobile. It should just be so versatile that the best experience is provided each time a visitor comes to your website. Those times are gone when it was okay to just have a computer compatible website and get conversions. Now mobile is no more a luxury and these changes need to be made to your online presence as well.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>Tips that directly improve page quality</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Understand the user&rsquo;s intent</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>As we all are aware of Google&rsquo;s effort to predict what we have searched for before we even finish typing. It took many years for it to reach there and now every website needs to focus on doing the same. Appear in Google&rsquo;s suggestions to a user&rsquo;s query. Matching your content to someone&rsquo;s search intent is a very important step. If someone is looking for information you don&rsquo;t want to send them to your products page but give them the right information. Getting this right will help in improving your page&rsquo;s quality score.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>CONTENT &ndash; Read Twice</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>A significant factor in enhancing your page quality is content. The content should be based on the right keyphrases by conducting keyword research. Thin content and duplicate content have no value for search engines and this just degrades your page quality. Try to become the source of information rather a referral to a competitor or a leader in your niche. This does not rule out keeping an eye on your competitors that always helps.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Build trust and goodwill</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>The transition of businesses to online stores and websites has increased the scope for all businesses but has also added a suspicion in the user\\&#39;s mind. Users are now puzzled about where to put their trust in and go for the purchase or any transaction for that matter. This is a major reason a business needs to show that it can be trusted and that you are an authority in your niche. Using testimonials is one such tab that builds trust and reliability on your brand. This also helps to improve your page quality directly.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Linking matters</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>All the pages on your website hold different content of value but guiding the crawler from one page to another is very important. Your links should appear in all pages of your website relevant to other pages on your website. Internal linking does matter when it comes to page quality and working on this will make a huge difference. But make sure to not go overboard with this internal linking this will not only piss off the customer but also the crawler may take this up as an unethical use of internal linking.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:quote -->\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>A <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/\">digital marketing company</a> takes up the best ways to get your brand the identity and limelight it requires in its niche. Finding the right people with the correct values is not difficult but challenging.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<!-- /wp:quote -->', 'We will discuss how to improve your page quality for SEO some extra love and what can be done to make them high-quality pages.', '10-tips-to-improve-your-page-quality-for-seo', 'Page Quality For SEO,SEO,Tips To Improve SEO', 'Mona', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 11:47:38');
INSERT INTO `blog` (`id`, `blog_title`, `blog_category`, `image1`, `image2`, `description`, `description1`, `blog_url`, `tags`, `author_name`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(11, 'Social Media SEO Tips to Increase Search Rankings', 'Social Media', 'social-media-seo-tips-to-increase-search-rankings-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The whole concept of digital marketing consists of mainly 4 aspects namely; Social Media, Search Engine, Website Development, and Content. They can be worked on separately but are tethered to one aspect as a whole. Considering social media madness that is ever-increasing today. Social media is closely related to SEO. They may not be directly proportional but surely have a positive impact on a business&rsquo;s rankings.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>The use of hashtags to get featured on Google search results is an efficient way to get that organic reach. When you search for a hashtag trend on google it displays twitter cards up in the zero spots. This enables hashtags to deliver the best search results to its users.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:pullquote -->\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>Your digital marketing campaign focussing on SEO will deliver better results if it is driven by your social media presence.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<!-- /wp:pullquote --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Here are some handy tips that may help you get more from your social media pages</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Audit your current social scenario</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>As yourself some questions as a marketer:</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list {\\\"ordered\\\":true} -->\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>How many conversions are driven by your social media?</li>\r\n	<li>Is your social media delivering a reliable ROI?</li>\r\n	<li>Which channels are driving you towards the best results?</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Measuring your ROI is one of the most important metrics that concern your social media efforts. When you have a clear hold on your ROI you can begin integrating SEO tricks into your social media activities. This will allow you to stretch your budget but also stick to your limits backed by some serious statistics.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Push SEO in SMO</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Your business profile on social media platforms is more than just a business name or a marketing message. This is the starting point for all your SEO efforts and giving them a strong backing. Your social media profile is your first impression to your audience. It should be enticing for your customers so that they visit your website and make a purchase. When someone searches for your business on google where does your name appear? These points can help you develop your business profile on social media and meet user&rsquo;s intent. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>3. Optimize social images for SEO</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Your profile on a <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/social-media-seo-tips-to-increase-search-rankings/\" target=\"\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;\">social networking platform</a> is all about images. Nothing speaks better than an image with information and some element that supports that information. Just adding these images will get you those likes and views on a social media platform. But did you know these images on social media can appear on the search by optimising them by adding alt text or filename?</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>4. Build relationships through engagement</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Relationships foster through trust and credibility and your response to your customer\\&#39;s query can help you build an alliance with them. When the customers sense you have interests in their struggles and pains it becomes easier to engage with them.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Not only by responding to them but asking them relevant questions to your brand will help you get their valuable opinions. Look at what they are posting their content on their pages and what they dislike.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>5. Use storytelling in your captions</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Whatever your business may be your content plays an important role in marketing. Content is compelling when a storytelling style is incorporated in it. Your captions are like an investment, enticing your customers through captions should be your priority. Add focus keywords and related keywords within the captions this helps the bot to read your content as per the ongoing trend. If there is a title section on your posts include these words in the title section itself.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>6. Make sharing easier</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Placing proper share buttons and compelling calls to action will share your content all over the platforms. These components on your blog will increase your reach and also help you get more followers. Also ensure that your content is share-worthy making it more appealing, engaging, and more helpful.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>7. Collaborate to increase the growth rate</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Look for brands with a similar niche that are growing just like your brand and interview them. Talk about their pain points and struggles in this niche and exchange your expertise. This does not mean revealing your trade secrets but this will show your customers how humble you are. It will reflect that competition does not drive you but the opportunity to serve them better is your motivation.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>8. Use Influencers for your branding</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s an era of online branding, marketing and selling as well. Thus, approaching influencers can be beneficial for your online brand. When these influencers share their trust with you and make-believe that your brand is a reliable one. The consumers tend to look up to you for their needs. Building strong relationships with niche-based influencers for a longer time will help you reap the benefits from their followers.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>9. Look for do-follow link giveaways</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Just like products and services some prominent platforms provide do-follow links. As you post your site links on your social media pages these links are reliable forms of people reaching your site. Leveraging from social media includes posting on sites such as Pinterest, Tumblr, Reddit and quora.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>10. Cross-promote your brand</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>One post can perform differently on various platforms. For example, a video post will do better on Instagram than on LinkedIn and Twitter. Adding a social media sidebar to your posts makes it easier for people to follow you on social media.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:quote -->\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>Many <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/\" target=\"\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;\">digital marketing companies</a> choose to guide their clients on social media and SEO separately Our word of advice would be to build a marketing strategy that focuses on both of them.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<!-- /wp:quote -->', 'let\'s see some handy Social Media SEO Tips that may help you get more from your social media pages.', 'social-media-seo-tips-to-increase-search-rankings', 'Social Media,Social Media SEO Tips,Increase Search Ranking', 'Mona', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 11:51:23'),
(12, 'SEO tips to Index and rank new content - FASTER!', 'SEO', 'seo-tips-to-index-and-rank-new-content-faster-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The best seo tips get Google&rsquo;s crawler on your website again and repeatedly is to have a very active and working blog. As you publish this novel content on your website you want it to be ranked and indexed in the SERPs and reap the benefits (traffic) as soon as possible. But the wait is never-ending and it is moreover a frustrating process. Few simple things you implement can help you nudge the crawler to index it faster and make it rank too. These include very basic and advanced steps that can help you get that SERPs position for your brand, Organically!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:quote -->\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>We will look at in three parts being Indexing and ranking together, indexing alone, and just ranking.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<!-- /wp:quote --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Let&rsquo;s dive right into it and check out these easy tips.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>Indexing and Ranking</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Linking in is Important</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Just by doing the basic being writing a new blog and publishing it on your website you want to make sure you add links to your content. Links to important pages lets emphasize this. Linking to your website pages that you want special attention to is an important factor. This is the basic step and you don&rsquo;t want to abandon those pages on your website. Such as your services page, the about page, it can be any such page that contains just the right information. Including these links in your post lets the crawler know that it is supposed to crawl these pages in the future. It creates a crawl queue for it. Google gets quality signals from these links that help it understand how to rank your page.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Revamp Old Content</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>A quick trick that shows us what is the rank of a particular page or website it by simply searching it against this prefix &lsquo;site:&rsquo; This allows you to determine relevant pages of your site that include target keywords and is now good targets to include in your newer posts. Your older posts generated a good amount of traffic with the old Google algorithm and calling it again through a crawler will get you that and more traffic.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Increased Sharing</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Content works best on all platforms because its optimisation is a prime focus for the leader of search engines &ndash; GOOGLE! Even though we add millions of content copies online we need to take extra efforts to push this content to the frontline to appear in relevant searches. This is clearly understood as the increase in competition has reduced the attention span of all consumers to almost nil. Hence, creating profiles on content aggregators such as Reddit helps you gain a higher authority over other content publishers. These aggregator sites enhance your added links for ranking and give external linking.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Direct traffic to URL</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>If you launch some new content and run it on Facebook ads it helps you drive a massive amount of traffic to your website. Even though you are paying for that traffic google measures that as valid traffic on your page. As this increases Google tracks it through Google Chrome and see the traffic being attracted by one source. Then they realise that this page is an important source of relevant information and it needs to be ranked.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Now that we have looked at indexing and ranking together</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Let&rsquo;s jump right into the indexing tips.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>Indexing</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>The old Fetch &amp; Render</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>We are all aware of the current Google Search URL Inspection Tool that was earlier known as the fetch and render. Google now simply allows you to submit an URL and tell them to crawl it. When you do that, they put that URL in priority crawl queue. This simply tells us that there is a list of URLs that Google crawls, it just digs in the priority list first and crawls them faster and indexes them.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Do you know Sitemaps?</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Everyone uses sitemaps and its now a basic of SEO and digital marketing practices as a whole. It is the easiest and quickest way to get your URLs indexed. Some more efforts in this process can make it more efficient and reap more benefits from submitting your sitemaps. Just type in google.com/ping and put in the sitemap with the URL. Google will instantly queue it in for crawling and all the URLs in there should get indexed easily if they meet the quality standards.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>The Indexing API</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>In the past few months, Google and bing have introduced new APIs to speed up the indexing processes. Both these solutions have the potential to allow indexing massively. You can submit 100s and 1000s of URLs via an API.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Now let&rsquo;s look at Ranking Tips separately to sum this piece up</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Once your content gets indexed you need to get to rank it faster.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>Ranking</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Manifest Search Clicks</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>As you drive traffic to the URL you can generate search clicks.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Instead of sharing a URL on Twitter, you can simply share a google result. People will click this link and it will take them to a Google result that has relevant keywords and rank. Instead of directly sharing the link to a new content share the search result link that is displaying that particular content. It helps you increase the CTR and also helps you rank for auto-suggest queries. So when people search for those keywords that are in your content your content will appear in those suggested links.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Create the content on fresh queries</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>When the user intents to search for something they expect the latest result on that. This simply means if I am looking for some trends in fashion, I simply mean the trends today not the trends from before. If I do want to look at previous trends, I will mention that in my search query. Hence, the work here is to search for queries that you want to write about and try to check what the latest post that appears. If you can generate a new copy for that query you will probably win that spot in the SERPs.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Pull crawlers through URL structure</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Many of us are aware of this tip and many are not but it is really important to use this for SEO. When you add a new page with a new page URL Google does see it but they do not have enough signals to support its ranking. As their announcements in the past have talked about how they leverage URL structure, it is important to read which structure ranked earlier. When you use the already existing structure it gets some temporary signals from the past to rank it.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:pullquote -->\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>This list does include effective tips any <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/\" target=\"\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;\">digital marketing company</a> or a marketing individual can use to create an effective impact on the SERPs. You may also have your inputs to this list and we would be delighted to hear from you.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<!-- /wp:pullquote -->', 'The best seo tips to get Googles crawler on your website again and repeatedly is to have a very active and working blog.', 'seo-tips-to-index-and-rank-new-content-faster', 'SEO Tips,SEO Tips To Index,Rank New Content', 'Mona', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 11:51:50'),
(13, 'Tips To Boost Video Rankings On Youtube | Increase YouTube Ranking', 'Youtube', 'tips-to-boost-video-rankings-on-youtube-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Boost Video Rankings On YouTube</strong> Most popular search engines consist of big names such a Google, Bing, Yahoo, and others. More than 2 billion active users monthly are on one such huge platform &ndash; Youtube.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>How Boost Video Rankings On YouTube</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>It is a <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/social-media-marketing/\" target=\"\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;\">social media platform</a> which now behaves like a traditional search engine. People&rsquo;s behaviour on Youtube is similar to something people do on Google. When you read and learn about SEO on search engines to rank your websites you come across all the rules that apply to them. Similar rules are applicable on Youtube search engine. Optimising video content is critical to ranking and attracting the audience. Finding the right keywords to communicate your content and design a good user experience is very important even on Google.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Here are some tools and tips that will come handy when you are trying to grow your Youtube presence.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Topics in trend on Google</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>A tool that works wonders for researching what the masses are looking for is Google Trends. When you specifically look for Youtube search it gives you the exact trends people are searching on Google. This data is sourced from Google that is a reliable source to be trusted.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Look for Keywords</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>The right place to look for keywords is the Youtube autocomplete feature. The moment you type in your query it predicts your search and this is what makes it the most effective medium to get relevant keywords.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Another relevant tool in this keyword search is the Google Ads keyword planner. You can enter your seed keywords and get a bunch of related keywords in this application.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>The right tags</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Using proper tags is the main aspect of boosting your rankings on Youtube. Tags are added by creators to put videos in relevant categories and make it easier for viewers to navigate.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Auditing your channel</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Look deeply in your success and failures. It will help you realise what is working for you and what is not. It will also help you audit your future opportunities for boosting your rankings on Youtube. Tubebuddy and Tubics is a similar tool to Youtube Analytics that has the same results that let you manage your page.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Keep your competitors close</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Tools like RivalIQ allow you to get a full profile of your competitors Youtube presence. It gives you an overview of their best performing videos according to category and location.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Optimise the comment section</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Even though the comments section is not a crucial <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/seo-optimization/\">SEO factor</a> but it indirectly affects your rankings. Comments can make or break your channel they affect your brand very deeply. Youtube has its feature that lets you moderate your comments and create a list of forbidden words.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:quote -->\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>These tips though less in number will help you navigate through the SEO requirements for your Youtube channel. You should think of Youtube SEO even before you upload a video this makes the task of uploading it more efficient.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<!-- /wp:quote --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'More than 2 billion active monthly users are on such huge platform  Youtube, so it is really important to Boost Video Rankings on YouTube.', 'tips-to-boost-video-rankings-on-youtube', 'YouTube Video Ranking,Boost Video Ranking,Increase Youtube Ranking', 'Mona', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 11:58:37'),
(14, 'Digital Marketing Trends 2021 | Trends to Watch in 2021', 'Digital Marketing', 'digital-marketing-trends-2021-trends-to-watch-in-2021-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Digital Marketing Trends 2021</strong> The year 2020 being a downfall for all businesses and professionals was something that was not expected. For community-minded people such as marketers, we need to collaborate across multiple departments. As we keep a track of our competitors in the market we are deeply entwined to the goals of our customers.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>It is better to look at the ongoing and upcoming insights for the upcoming year and be prepared for a drastic change in the marketing industry. There is a diverse circle of ideas but one common goal to these ideas is the thought of a better future. <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/marketing-strategy/\">Marketing in 2021</a> is going to be more empathetic as ever and evolve with the power of positivity.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>The power of a marketer can be used for both good and evil, to err is to human. After all marketers are humans serving humans. We need to work toward making brands more trustworthy. Building a relationship of love and kindness with brands and generate a loyal customer.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>Let&rsquo;s look at what 2021 has in store based on fabulous predictions by marketing experts.</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>The Virtual Shift</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Live events have proven to be miraculous for brands suffering the wrath of Covid. Your prospects will be driven towards these kinds of events and engage with you through them. Newest was when Netflix met Slack and there was on-demand live streaming of videos playing on-site. Not only can you connect with your prospects but such platforms allow them to interact with each other and relate to the problems in their lives.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Building a community</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>We have all attended out annual general meetings or a grand annual event virtually this year. As these shifts make people comfortable around them it also allows them to bond with its attendees. Singular events with fewer people focussing on one thing at a time are a no-go now. Reliable and verified sources sharing valuable information are valued as community leaders and can create a greater impact. People are now looking for value addition and a company should look forward to adding practical values to conversations.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>New ways of online interaction</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Many brands did take the virtual shift and move their events online but many failed miserably. Their failure was the fault of replicating the live event experience on an outdated model of software. Everyone is on Zoom and now creating something called &lsquo;zoom fatigue&rsquo;. Companies are now wondering how to target this crowd online and engage before and after an event online. The demand for engagement is premier this year and organisations should focus on building meaningful as well as long-lasting connections with their audiences.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Inclusivity is a necessity</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Virtual events that try to mimic in-person events caused a huge spike in registrations and attendance at the beginning of the pandemic. But this flow of numbers lasted only for one or two months. People are now looking for human interactions, rather than a sit-in conference. Webinars are just no acceptable nowadays. The audience wants discussions in panels in which they can ask questions so that they can get their action on what is happening in the meeting. First, we only promised that it will be an interactive session but today as we are in 2021 it is a necessity.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Customer King pushes Brands Ahead</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Alignment of the sales marketing and customer service team leads to optimum customer satisfaction. Many challenges of the revenue teams have resolved when they have applied a customer-centric approach. Due to the pandemic norms, we cannot rely on traditional methods of meeting people in-person. But we can work towards bringing our customers close and attending to their pain points to build a winning relationship.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Brand Navigation</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>The movement of a brand through thick political influences becomes difficult. A worldwide pandemic at hand is pushing marketers to make tough decisions about the alignment of their customers with marketing goals. Your potential customers will invest their money in you only after they figure what your take is on the current ongoing scenario in the country. Be it the political fiasco or how you are handling the pandemic. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>A/B Testing is out</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>With the indulgence of AI into marketing, we cannot predict trends before they even take place. Spending on A/B testing is wasteful and going obsolete. It is nowhere encouraged by marketers all over the world. For testing the performance of a particular format one can still rely on these techniques but using them for paid ads has no meaning anymore.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The year 2020 being a downfall for all businesses was something that was not expected, now let\'s see Digital Marketing Trends in 2021.', 'digital-marketing-trends-2021-trends-to-watch-in-2021', 'Digital Marketing,Digital Marketing Trends,Digital Marketing Trends 2021', 'Mona', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 11:54:17'),
(15, '5 Best and Viable Digital Marketing SEO Trends for 2021', 'Digital Marketing', 'digital-marketing-seo-trends-for-2021-1-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>SEO Trends In Digital Marketing</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Digital marketing </strong>cannot be fruitful if the SEO of the overall system is weak and lags behind its competitors on the market. The web is a vast space, and people worldwide have access to the internet. Having a robust SEO layout can be immensely beneficial for a company or business firm in digital marketing.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Every day, billions of web searches are made on search engine platforms. However, only a fraction of these users find the marketing strategies attractive enough to visit the advertiser\\&#39;s website. As a result, businesses lose millions of potential customers every day. Here is this segment; you will come to know the best strategies and trends that will allow your SEO framework to work efficiently.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>5 Best Digital marketing SEO Trends for 2021</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>As mentioned earlier, <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/what-is-seo/\">SEO is crucial </a>to attracting potential customers and clients to your website. Having a weak or vague approach towards this subject may be highly punishing and may even incur losses over the company. Thus, you are highly suggested to follow and implement the mentioned SEO trends to make sure online business is fruitful and sustainable for the coming years too.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Analyzing the behavioral patterns of users</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>It is vital to understand the behavioral patterns of internet users as every one of them is a potential customer. Every day there are billions of Google searches on the internet, and the most relevant answer to their questions is recommended first. As such, it is highly recommended for firms and online service providers to become relevant and try to win people\\&#39;s trust at an early stage. This is to promote your services in Google searches, but your company will also begin to attract permanent clients looking for quality content.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Focusing on clients\\&#39; interests will ensure that your website is regularly visited by enough people so that you get recommended quite often. Carrying out this strategy efficiently will soon land your services amongst the top answers from various search engines. So, it is time that brands and online service providers start focusing on customer concerns.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Tracking Brand SERPs</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>It is a well-known fact that search engines such as Google have well-researched facts about their users. The type of content you consume on the internet or the items you search for play a crucial role in integrating this complete procedure as only similar brands and services are more likely to be recommended to you.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>This ecosystem of preferences plays a considerable role for digital marketing companies as well. The more diverse a company is in its approach, the greater will be the number of consumers it has. It is diversifying to various other linked social platforms such as YouTube or Facebook to ensure that your brand reaches more potential customers every day.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>3. Optimizing the web experience for your users</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>An inconvenient web experience such as a slow website or an irresponsive interface can intervene in the decisions made by the users. As such, focusing heavily upon the user satisfaction quotient can prove rewarding in the long run. Websites play a crucial role in executing digital marketing strategies. Moreover, any discrepancies in this field can result in the loss of interest amongst customers.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Brands are suggested to focus on implementing web designs that are very quick to load and highly responsive. Moreover, launching a suitable platform for mobile devices is also recommended as most web users rely on mobile devices regularly. Thus, even if your brand\\&#39;s website is highly optimized but relatively inefficient for mobile devices, it can be positively punishing.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>4. Focus on automation</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>It is a known fact that automated services and AI-controlled tasks are more efficient than manual approaches. Brands of today\\&#39;s age should focus intensely upon the advantages of automation and AI-driven tasks. As such, manual workload can turn out to be a mishap at any point, and being an individual, you can only focus on so many tasks at hand.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>As a result, there could be errors in interpreting data analytics or even while serving clients. However, automation will allow your firm to work with the highest efficiency without thinking of mistakes. Moreover, an AI-driven service can be outsourced and replicated for several tasks, and thus, interacting with thousands of online customers will become seamless.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>5. Make your SEO structure scalable</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Giving enough thought and effort towards the scalability of the SEO structure can be a game-changer for any brand. As such, you have fixed notions in your online firm that constitute particular segments that will make your business model an efficient one. Also, it will increase the probability of gaining profits in the long run.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Here are the basics of scaling and managing your services:</strong><br />\r\nScaling up your SEO structure and your business propaganda can be fruitful in many ways, and there are some basics to keep in mind to execute this plan successfully.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list {\\\"ordered\\\":true} -->\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>You have a detailed report of all the work that goes around in your business and scraping off those that can be easily automated. This will help you get a clearer picture.</li>\r\n	<li>It is setting up tools that determine the ranks of your current URL keywords. This will ensure that your services are well-promoted irrespective of the shifts in generic keywords.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\r\n\r\n<h4>Conclusion</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>The year 2021 will be a crucial year for all the brands that focus on digital marketing. However, to get ahead of the herd and make sure your services are well-received in the market, set goals. Moreover, staying consistent with it is the key. However, with the current shifts in online markets, it is also recommended to be highly agile in business strategies and SEO layouts.<br />\r\nIn this segment, all the major SEO trends for 2021 have been mentioned and discussed briefly. If you manage to work around the mentioned fields effectively, your brand is sure to receive the attention it deserves. However, retaining your customers is also pretty crucial. Also, there are specific protocols to abide by to make sure your brand achieves the trust of customers and clients.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nLastly, being consistent even with the shifts in business management is the key to success. Thus, all marketing companies are recommended to pay attention to even the smallest of details.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Digital marketing cannot be fruitful if the SEO of the overall system is weak and lags behind its competitors on the market.', 'digital-marketing-seo-trends', 'Digital Marketing,Digital Marketing Trends,Search Engine Optimization', 'Jewel', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 11:55:40'),
(16, 'Importance Of Reddit In Digital Marketing | Get Free Traffic', 'Digital Marketing', 'importance-of-reddit-in-digital-marketing-get-free-traffic-1-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Importance of Reddit </strong>Marketers have unleashed the <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/social-media-marketing/\">power of social media</a> for some time now. Every company, big or small, has its social media presence. This also has helped them garner a lot of traffic and, in turn, sales for their companies. However, the trend now seems to change a bit, and not all marketers are taking over. So, instead of the promotions that previously used to be the key point in the sales campaign, it has now changed to word of mouth.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nWith this changed perception among the audience, the best platforms that would help you have the upper hand would be Quora and Reddit. Both the platforms talk about the user experience and help clear the doubts that one might have about a product. These platforms also give the users a lot to talk about, and the readers have a targeted audience. In this article, let us understand how you can make yourself stand out on Reddit.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>What is Reddit</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Before you get your hands dirty with the marketing techniques you need in this particular platform, you must know what this platform is all about. So, Reddit promotes itself as the \\&quot;front page of the internet\\&quot;. This was mainly because they started with their primary focus on social news. However, off late, you would instead call it a forum. One that is used for almost everything that you can think of.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>There are as many as 1 million communities in Reddit for about 51 million registered users. So, you can well understand that there is almost certainly a community for your product or service.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>Reddit and Marketing</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Marketing in Reddit is something that would need discipline. If you are starting with your journey in Reddit as a marketer, we have a few cents that would help you. Check out the following:</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>1. Choose The Community Wisely. When you choose the community, make sure that you choose one where you can sell your product. Also, make sure that you have the perfect audience to target.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>2. Give More Than You Take: When in Reddit, remember that you should give in more to the community than you take out of it. So, in any community, make sure that you give in some relevant information or knowledge 80% of the time and promote yourself not more than 20% of the time. This would help you have a better authenticity level and would be at a state to drive in more visitors.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>3. Be Genuine And Engage With Members: So, when you share an experience or a story, try to make sure that you are as much genuine with it as you can. Also, try to engage with the members, try responding to their questions, try to interact.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>4. Grow Organically: Marketers are almost always in a hurry. If you too are, then Reddit is not the right place for you. Make sure that you are growing organically. We mean that you are not asking your friends, employees, or colleagues to upvote your answers or create fake accounts for the same. Reddit communities are harsh against this.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>So, these would help you have the best time on Reddit. However, also remember that Reddit is a platform in which men dominate. As per the report published by Ignite, the highest number of Reddit users is 35-44, and they are predominantly male. Most users have a bachelor\\&#39;s degree and have an income range of between $25,000-$50,000 per year.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>This information would help you better understand the type of audience you would be dealing with in Reddit.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Get Tons Of Free Reddit Traffic</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>The only reason why you are on Reddit is to get traffic. Well, we do understand that, but make sure that the communities should not understand that. That is the key to benefit from Reddit. It would be best if you promoted in a way that nobody should understand that you are here for promotions. So here are a few dos and don\\&#39;ts Reddit that would help you get loads of free traffic to help you convert.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>1. Understand the audience. Ensure that you share the correct bit of information in the perfect form to the right audience. Reddit is not any other social media platform. It\\&#39;s not like you can go about putting in your banners or your story everywhere, every community has its own set of rules, and some might not accept an image or a bulky text in their community.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>2. Do Not Just Promote: Remember that you should not just promote and promote as stated above. You should share something meaningful with the community members and then try to engage with them and then make a subtle promotion once in a while.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>3. Understand How To Promote: Now, this becomes important. Understand how you can and how you want to promote. Is it that you want to promote out and out? Is it how it\\&#39;s done in the community? If not, do you want to put in your story stating how it helped you with your problem? Well, you can only decide the same from the community.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>4. Learn From The Successful Campaigns: Check out the successful promotions of others in the community. Try to understand what they are doing better than others who are failing to reach the goal. Now, once you understand the key to a successful campaign, get your campaigns in line. Keep learning from others\\&#39; mistakes and don\\&#39;t repeat them with yourself.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Remember these bits of do\\&#39;s and don\\&#39;ts. This would help you get the best out of your Reddit campaigns. However, at times the mix becomes very crucial. Almost always, it\\&#39;s very crucial and critical. So, to help yourself with the same, you might get in touch with a really good digital marketing company. They would help ease your problems when it comes to Reddit. XYZ company is one of the most reputed in town. You can try them out for your needs.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Reddit and Digital Marketing</strong></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Well, in this era of Marketing, Reddit plays a significant role. It can further be concluded that Reddit is the 7th most viewed website globally and 6th in the United States. This means that you should not have a digital marketing strategy without Reddit. At the same time, the bounce rate of the website is much low when it considered that it has about 1.7 billion views per month.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>This means that you are losing out on 1.7 billion eye-balls unless you are present on the platform. Overall, Reddit is a platform that would help you have a targetted audience base, and that would thus help you have an inflated market base. However, expert help in this particular domain would only make things easier and less time-consuming for you!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>So, we hope that we could help you with how exactly Reddit can help you achieve your goals for digital marketing. However, if you still feel that there is something that we did miss out on or if you want to ask anything to us directly, please feel free to connect with us in the comment section. Hope that you have a successful run in Reddit! If not, we at iDotcommers are always ready to make it successful!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Reddit promotes itself as the \"front page of the internet\" so before posting on reddit we should know what is the importance of Reddit', 'importance-of-reddit', 'Digital Marketing,Reddit,Reddit Marketing', 'Jewel', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 12:11:59');
INSERT INTO `blog` (`id`, `blog_title`, `blog_category`, `image1`, `image2`, `description`, `description1`, `blog_url`, `tags`, `author_name`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(17, 'Video Marketing Strategy | Marketing Videos For Business', 'Digital Marketing', 'video-marketing-strategy-marketing-videos-for-business-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Video Marketing</strong> It is a fast-paced world. That is just the reason why the black and white traditional forms of marketing, precisely the banners, the newspaper advertisements, and the posters, are all losing their charm. People need something exciting, something exciting day in day out. In an urge to meet with this growing need for excitement, the marketing industry as a whole has shifted to videos.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>However, not only has the marketing evolved. But over the years, a whole new genre of marketing, video marketing, has developed and has established a resounding market base. So, let us now try to understand the nuances of video marketing.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Video marketing is simply marketing your products or goods or services by a video. This means that instead of the old marketing gimmicks where you could just put in a few pictures of the product and explain your worth in writing, you can now have a video that would resonate with the customers. This is a marketing strategy that is on the rise.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>If you look around you, you come across video marketing every day on your social media, websites, and even on billboards these days. And yes, they are beating the traditional marketing techniques by quite a margin.<br />\r\nLet us now understand the best video marketing strategy. Before getting into the video marketing strategy, you would need to understand why you need the strategy.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Thumb rule of Marketing</strong></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>In a given amount of resources, we would have to get the best possible outcome. This means that we would have to prioritize where exactly we want to spend our resources. Now, when it comes to video marketing, you would have to understand your limitations and constraints.<br />\r\nWith the resources, would you be able to market the videos on all social media?<br />\r\nDo you want to capture the attention on your website?<br />\r\nAlso, what are the best platforms from where you get the best conversions!<br />\r\nSo now, how would you exactly get the perfect video marketing strategy?<br />\r\nIf you are here, then in all possibility, you are yet to kiss the perfect blend of the marketing strategy that would suit your business.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Here, let us understand a few pointers that you should ponder when you get started.</strong></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:list {\\\"ordered\\\":true} -->\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Understand your goal. Set the goal for yourself and be realistic, please!</li>\r\n	<li>Understand your target audience. So, if you are selling the best beard oil, make sure you target men above 18 possibly!</li>\r\n	<li>Figure out the problem that you are solving and spin a story around it. Understand the problem that you solve. This would help you understand what exactly you want to convey in your videos.</li>\r\n	<li>Stick to the timeline and be practical and punctual. Now, please don\\&#39;t be disheartened or overjoyed with the initial response. If you have decided on a timeline for yourself, stick to it.</li>\r\n	<li>And finally, Allocate the budget and stick to it. Make sure that you have realistic expectations from the budget that you set aside. But at the same time, make sure that you do not overspend to meet the goal.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Once you have done all the above, you would have to sit down and analyze. Remember to get the most suitable marketing strategy for your videos. One thing that you would have to do regularly is to analyze. Analyze and understand what is working for you and what is not. Filter out what is working best for you and move on with it! This would make sure that with every passing campaign, you would become more cost-effective.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Video marketing helps you have a better impact on your target audience. As it has been proved much time in the past, the audio-video effects have a more decisive influence on the human mind than the audio or pictorial forms. So, your videos would more likely leave a better impact.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>SEO is the new buzzword of the market these days. The videos are an SEO goldmine. Your search engine would almost always value videos over other content forms.<br />\r\nProduct description videos are much more loved and followed as compared to the product description. That says volume about the practice already.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Tools For Video Marketing</strong></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Video Marketing Blaster</strong>: this application would help you have your video on the first page of your search engine. You can also find some of the best keywords with this app.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Video</strong>: It\\&#39;s super easy to create videos with this app! You would love it right from the first use. So, if you are starting with your video skills, then this is the app you should be looking at.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Animaker</strong>: It has one of the most significant numbers of animated videos in its arsenal. Also, it is one of those applications that is being used by Google, Uber, Walmart, and others. So, if some of the best in the business can trust the application, you definitely can!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hippo Video</strong>: If you want to do video email campaigning, this is just the application you have been looking for. It would give you the much-needed information for your campaigns. Never forget, you can also have video support and video hosting features among the other services by the software.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Think of Audio modulation and imagination at the same time. Imagine that you are listening to an advertisement on the radio or reading about it in a newspaper. You cannot see the product in the first place, and in the second case, you read a plain text with no emotions. When you combine the best of the two, you see a product and get a voice modulation that guides your emotions. Imagine how powerful the tool would be. That is exactly what video marketing is.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>You are reducing your concentration span. With all the glam and glitter that the world has to offer, your concentration span reduces with every passing day. So, to make sure that you can attract the concentration of your viewer, you need to have an edge, and that edge can only be given by video marketing. This also explains the reason why product videos are becoming more popular than product descriptions.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>Benefits Of Video Marketing</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Finally, with all that, let us try to boil down to the video marketing benefits.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list {\\\"ordered\\\":true} -->\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>To start with, it attracts more eyeballs and thus helps in better brand recollection. Videos in every form are much more accepted and retained by the viewers.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The cost involved in the video marketing campaign is low.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Overall, video marketing is something that is here to stay, and with the passing days, it would only get more relevant. In today\\&#39;s world, the next big thing in the marketing domain would possibly be 3-D video marketing. To ensure that you don\\&#39;t miss the bus, you should start with video marketing soon! If you want to point out something that we have missed, please feel free to comment below. Also, if you want us to manage all your video marketing needs, don&rsquo;t hesitate to contact us. We at <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/\">iDotcommers</a> can help your reach your marketing goals faster!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Video marketing is simply marketing your products or goods or services by a video. This is a marketing strategy that is on the rise.', 'video-marketing', 'Video Marketing,Video Marketing Strategy,Video Marketing For Business', 'Jewel', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 12:19:01'),
(18, 'What is IGTV video on Instagram | IGTV Marketing Strategy', 'Social Media', 'what-is-igtv-video-on-instagram-igtv-marketing-strategy-1024x576.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>before talking about <strong>IGTV Videos</strong> lets explore the role of videos, Videos are something that is taking over the written content. Vlogs are the new-age blogs. Then be it the how-to guides or fat-loss tutorials or the technical nuances. Videos are taking over the written industry like a storm. With this storm around, the entire marketing focus is now changing. The major shift is from the written content to the video vlogs.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Among the many social media platforms that have lost almost their identity amid this change, a few have tried hard to adapt to it. One such platform is Instagram. The new IGTV network allows users to upload their videos and doesn&rsquo;t have any time limit to upload and showcase.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Use IGTV For Marketing</strong></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>IGTV is one of those tools that you should use for marketing. The basic reason behind this is that with this particular tool, you get a chance to showcase your video in multiple places on Instagram. Instagram is one of the most popular <a href=\"https://idotcommers.com/social-media-marketing/\">social media</a> platforms. Also, it might well be regarded as one of the most user-friendly platforms.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>All you would need to do in IGTV is find out the niche market that you fit in perfectly. Once you have that, you should now understand how you should start with your marketing campaign.<br />\r\nYou would also need to understand what works best for your audience and make them watch your video among the multiple options they would have in the network.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>So, for IGTV marketing, you should get in touch with the best influencers of your niche. This would help you smoothen the process and reduce the efforts manifolds. An influencer is one who the people on IGTV or Instagram widely follow. This would mean that they resonate a chord with people who are your target audience.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>IGTV Marketing Strategy</strong></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>When you talk about the<a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/marketing-strategy/\"> marketing strategy</a> of IGTV Video, it is rather straightforward, as long as you are not expecting immediate results. However, if you are in a hurry, then there are a few tricks that you would have to look up at while publishing your videos.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>To start with, you should make sure that the videos are not too lengthy. This is of utmost importance. People generally tend to avoid very long videos for channels that they do not connect to. At the same time, it becomes challenging to capture your audience\\&#39;s attention for a longer time.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Make sure that you are not always promoting. This is important. Make sure that you are not just promoting. So, what is the best way that you can go about it? You can start up with the problem that your product or service solves and then provide a real solution to it and finally promote your product or service. So, have a very subtle approach.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Analyze and understand. This is again something that you would need to take note of. After you are done with promoting one particular campaign, try to understand and analyze your mistakes. Check if and how you can correct them, and then go on once again. So, the analysis part is a constant.<br />\r\nTry to be as interactive as you can. You can have an AMA session where you can go on to answer questions that you might have from the possible leads. You might also go for a simple Q&amp;A.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Post Customer stories at regular intervals. This would help develop trust for yourself on the platform. So, your customers would have a proper understanding of the type of service or products you offer.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>IGTV Marketing In A Nutshell</strong></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>You know what and how IGTV video can help you in your marketing, and you do also understand why you should not miss out on IGTV. I have tried to give you the basic info about perfectly everything related to IGTV. You should make the call on your efforts and resource allocation to IGTV specifically, but make sure that you do not do away with the platform.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>I could answer almost every doubt that you had about IGTV video. If you have any more doubts that you want us to clear for you, please feel free to please let us know!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'IGTV video is best tool for marketing. with this particular tool, you get a chance to showcase your video in multiple places on Instagram.', 'what-is-igtv-video', 'IGTV For Marketing,IGTV Marketing Strategy,IGTV Videos,What Is IGTV', 'Jewel', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 13:09:55'),
(19, 'Influencer Marketing | Strategy And Platforms Of Influencer Marketing', 'Influencer Marketing', 'influencer-marketing-strategy-and-platforms-of-influencer-marketing-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Promoting your product is something that you need to be good at. At the end of the day, even the best products would not see a buyer unless it\\&#39;s well promoted. With the passing days, the scope of promoting a product is changing. In recent times, influence marketing is one domain of advertising that garners a lot of attention from one and all.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2>What is influencer marketing</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Influencer marketing</strong> is simply a promotional technique where the brands get in touch with popular social media users or bloggers who have a large, engaged audience. These social media users or bloggers are known as influencers, and the marketing technique is known as influencer marketing.<br />\r\nThe main reason people or marketers go for influencer marketing is, in turn, to drive in more sales and also help in increasing brand awareness. Influencers play a vital role in both of them. In recent years it seems to be one of the best promotional techniques.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Influencers Marketing Platforms</strong></h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>You would find influencers in almost every platform, then be it vlogs or blogs and definitely on <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/social-media-marketing/\">social media platforms.</a> Also, the influencers are present on various platforms. However, now that you have to choose an influencer, you should first choose a platform. So let us try to understand which platform would be the best one for you.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>To start with, Facebook is one platform where it\\&#39;s tough to get a concentrated audience. Most people on Facebook have a minimal attention span, and the charm that the social media platform had once has faded out quite a bit.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Next up, Twitter and LinkedIn are too professional, and you would generally avoid them unless you are actually into a very serious product. So, we would strike that off the list, considering that you are not about to promote something severe.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>YouTube and Snapchat are options, but then you can only upload videos there. So, it might just become a constraint at times. So, we strike them off too.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>The best platform to help you market your product or services is Instagram. It\\&#39;s simple to use. It is one of the most popular social media platforms. You can post images and videos both. This is an advantage that is exactly what a marketer wants. You can put in pictures or videos, either of which helps you connect with the audience.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>So, we would try to help you understand how exactly you can promote your brand on Instagram. Some professional companies like <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/\">iDotcommer</a> offer digital marketing strategies to help you have the best out of your campaigns. They can help you save a lot of time and effort, and the results of their promotions are excellent, and they do have some of the best connections in the industry.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Influencer Marketing Strategy</strong></h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>You should keep in mind a few things when you go on with your marketing strategy. Firstly, make sure that the influencer you choose has the exact niche that you want to target. Also, make sure that followers count not everything you are looking forward to when selecting an influencer. You should understand the impact that he has on his followers and the niche that he is in.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Secondly, understand what would go best for the product you have and the influencer you are about to engage with. You think that a 5-minute video would work best, or should you go for a simple picture? This is something that you need to figure out yourself.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Lastly, understand the appeal. This is something that you need to be sure of. Understand the appeal. Why are you doing the promotion? Is it for promotions or sales, or do you want to help in brand awareness? Make sure that you have the perfect understanding of your proposition. It should not be that you go on to post something and expect something else.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>These strategies would help you get the best out of your entire promotional campaign. Overall these three-pointers would help you get the best audience and target groups. So make sure that you follow and implement them in your strategy.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\r\n\r\n<h4>Social Media Influencer Marketing</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Social media influencers are here to stay, and we would benefit from them for years to come. However, you would need to understand how you can make the most and also understand who can help you in getting the best results.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>We hope that this blog could help you understand the finest things about influencer marketing.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Influencer marketing is simply a promotional technique where the brands get in touch with popular social media users or bloggers', 'influencer-marketing', 'Influencer Marketing,Influencer Marketing Strategy,What Is Influencer Marketing', 'Jewel', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 12:20:18'),
(20, 'Online Reputation Management For Digital Marketing', 'Digital Marketing', 'online-reputation-management-for-digital-marketing-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Online Reputation Management is something that you might have heard about in recent years if you are a marketer or if you have a business even. Online Reputation Management (ORM) is one of the new marketing techniques that is helping the marketers in perfectly everything. Then be it the search engine results or be the online traffic. ORM has an impact on perfectly everything.<br />\r\nSo, now that you understand the importance that ORM has in marketing these days let us understand how this can help you. Then, we\\&#39;ll tell you how you can get the most out of this technique. So, let us try and understand ORM.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Online Reputation Management&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Online reputation management is a way by which one can manage their presence online. This means that you have the opportunity to help make sure that your audience sees the perfect bit of yourself when they search for you online. ORM is one way you can help happy customers promote your brand and let others understand your worth.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>So, how exactly do you make sure that you are at the best of your business when it comes to ORM. Well, it\\&#39;s not simple. You would have to make sure that you are kind, polite, and well-articulated when you are carrying on with your ORM. But remember that ORM is not always upfront. In fact, in most cases, it\\&#39;s a very subtle thing that you end up doing. In this way, you attract a lot of attention from your probable leads.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>The other thing that you need to understand and remember is never to play around with your customer. By that, what we mean is always make sure that you are honest to your customers and authentic too. So, help make sure that you have the best reviews, but even if you get some negative reviews, do not delete them or ignore them. Instead, accept them politely and try to incorporate the change required.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Apart from these, there is one more thing that is of utmost importance. While you accept the positives and the negatives by the customer, make sure that you showcase the best reviews first. This would help make sure that any new visitor who is searching for a similar product finds you in the right light. These are some of the most basic points that you would have to keep in mind while getting along with your ORM strategy. However, there are many more nuances that you can expect an experienced digital marketing manager to help you with.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>If you do not have a digital marketing manager already, then the best way to go about it is to hire an agency that can help you in it. Agencies are generally more cost-efficient than hiring an individual. At the same time, an agency provides a lot of experience and multiple resources to get your work done. So, if you are looking for one agency that can help you most with the ORM, then we would recommend <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/\">iDotcommers</a> for the great professional attitude that they have towards their work. They are young, dedicated, and energetic with tons of passion for what they do!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>Difference Between <strong>ORM and BRM&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>BRM stands for Brand Reputation Management. This is part of management where you make sure that your brand image is perfectly suited for your potential customers. To ensure that you have the brand reputation management in place, ORM plays a very important role. In recent years, if there is one thing that the youth looks forward to while making any purchase, then it is online on some platform or the other. So, managing your online presence in the best light would help you in managing your brand image online in this case. Also, you would help drive sales. If you are delivering an experience that you don\\&#39;t want your customers to forget, then for sure, the ORM is something that you should look forward to. Understand that if you offer the best Valentine\\&#39;s Day dinner, you promise an experience. If more people are promoting that experience and hailing you for the same, you have better chances to have a better company image.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Online Reputation Management Tools&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>It is recommended that you get in touch with a pro in this particular field. However, if you are unable to, you might look on with some of the tools you have to work on. To start with, Social Mention. This is one of the websites that would perfectly give you all the information you need to know about your brand. The various trackers that are present on the website help you have a clear understanding of what you need. It gives you an idea of what is going correct for you on social media platforms. The next in line would be Chat meter.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>This would help you understand and analyze the customer feedback that you get from various sources. Thus, it would improve the customer experience. This is something which is a must in case you don\\&#39;t have an expert to help you. The third and most important one would be Google Alert. Simply enter your company name on the website and get an alert over email. You can set the frequency to whatever suits you. Accordingly, you can check the best results. These three tools would help you immensely in helping you understand your journey on social media.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>ORM For Digital Marketing</strong></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>We hope to help you with a clear idea of what exactly ORM is and how it can change your brand value overall. The basics of ORM, why it is needed, and the best practices you can have while doing an ORM. Also, the tools that you might need if you are going to help yourself with the marketing. However, we would recommend that you take professional help in this regard.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>So, we do hope that now you understand the importance of ORM. It would help you uplift your business in the best way possible. With that, we would complete the article, hoping that you could learn something new from this. We would also hope you would let us know how we can help you in a better way. Let us know your comments, questions, or queries in the comment box below.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Online Reputation Management is something that you might have heard about in recent years if you are a marketer or if you have a business.', 'online-reputation-management', 'Online Reputation Management,ORM,ORM For Digital Marketing,Digital Marketing', 'Jewel', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 12:20:45'),
(21, 'What is core Web vitals why it is important | How are they measured', 'Google Updates', 'what-is-core-web-vitals-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Google Core Web Vitals</strong> There are more than 1.1 billion websites that are available on the World Wide Web. This means that when you search for something, it\\&#39;s quite possible that your search engine\\&#39;s algorithm would take around to select the best among these to help you with your query. So, the race that we have here is to be visible and be relevant to the users.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>To help the users have the best experience, each search engine has its own set of secret parameters that it traces to help rank a website. These various factors that search engines take into account are <strong>known as the Core Web Vitals.</strong> Since we all know that the most popular search engine that we have around is Google, we would mostly talk about Google and how it helps in ranking pages. This would help you understand the factors that would help you rank your website better and faster.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Important factors for Google Core Web Vitals</strong></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>When we talk about the parameters that Google looks out at, there are not too many, but just three. However, there are various finer parameters on these broader ones that make the equation more complicated. However, since we would try to overview the factors, we would discuss the three broad categories to help you grasp the requirement.<br />\r\nThe three factors that need to be mentioned would be some of the following:</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list {\\\"ordered\\\":true} -->\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Loading Times</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Interactivity (i.e., Page Responsiveness)</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Visual Page Stability</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Let us now try to understand each of these in detail and the matrices used to gauge them. This would help you understand the process better and make the entire journey more accessible to the top of the pages.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Loading Time:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>This you must have already understood. The name itself is pretty much self-explanatory. So, the faster your page loads, the better rankings you get on google, and the easier it is for people to notice you!<br />\r\nThe metric used by Google for checking this out is called the Largest Contentful Paint (LCP). So, let us try to understand how the metric work.<br />\r\nThe LCP helps measure the loading time that the users experience. You can term this as the time between clicking on a link and when the desired page opens up with sizable content on the screen.<br />\r\nWhat sets the LCP apart from most others of its type is that the LCP is possibly the only metric that checks the amount of time the page takes to open up in front of actual users, unlike most other metrics. Also, you must note here it\\&#39;s not just about the visibility of your page but also how much of it is interactive.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Interactivity (Page Responsiveness):</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>When you land on any website, if you have carefully noticed or if there is a visible lag in the page, you would have seen that although some functionalities are visible, they are not outright useable. This includes the likes of menus, clicking on some internal links and much more, you might see that the functionalities are not working at all for a few seconds till the page loads completely. The faster the page is interactive, the better it is for your website.<br />\r\nFirst, Input Delay is the metric that is used to understand the performance of this particular point. Now, let us try to understand the metric in detail.<br />\r\nAs per the tracker, if your website is fully responsive within 100 milliseconds, then you would have a good rating. The rating would be average in case you are above 100 and below 300 milliseconds. For websites above 300 milliseconds and below 500, they would be termed as poor. If you have a website where you mostly deal with content, it\\&#39;s quite possible that you would not have to worry much about this metric as it would take care of itself. But if you have a login or a signup page, then this metric becomes important.<br />\r\nIf you are using a signup or login page, make sure that you have a real light page and do not put in other heavy stuff like videos or heavy images. This would substantially help you in reducing the load time. However, there are a few other things you would have to keep in mind, but we would get into the details in future articles.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>3. Visual Page Stability:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>In simple terms, do the elements of your page move when the page is loading? If your answer is yes, then you would have to take care of it. If the answer is a no, then they are already taken care of. So, while the page loads, the elements of your page must be stable, and they should not hover around. This helps prevent the users from clicking on the wrong elements or even clicking on the same elements twice.<br />\r\nCumulative Layout Shift (CLS) is the metric that is used to gauge this particular parameter. The metric gauges how much your elements move. For a movement below 0.1 on the CLS scale, you would be in shape. On exceeding that, till 0.25, you should try to improve your website CLS. If your CLS is beyond 2.5, you should try to get it better!<br />\r\nSo, in this article, we tried to explain the various core web vitals and how exactly each one of them and measured. It is also essential for you to understand how you can help yourself have a better ranking by improving all these matrices. The ideas that you might be needing would be discussed in the subsequent articles. Some make sure that you keep a close eye on our blogs!<br />\r\nUnderstanding the Google Core Web Vitals is a challenging job. Thus, if you do not have much knowledge in the same, you can definitely refer to <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/\">iDotcommers</a>. They are professional, innovative, and have the perfect solution to all your needs.<br />\r\nPlease let us know if there is anything you want us to add or remove from the article above. Also, do let us know if there is any query that you might be having. We would love to address each of your questions individually!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Each search engine has its own set of secret parameters that it traces to help rank a website. known as the Core Web Vitals', 'core-web-vitals', 'Core Web Vitals,Google Core Web Vitals', 'Jewel', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 12:22:41'),
(22, 'Best Tools To Help Improve Your Google Core Web Vitals', 'Google Updates', 'tools-to-improve-core-web-vitals-1024x536.png', NULL, '<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Tools To Improve Google Core Web Vitals</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Here we bring to you the third article of its kind, related to the web vitals. Now that you know<a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/core-web-vitals/\"> What is core Web vitals</a> and also how you can <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/core-web-vitals-in-2021/\">master your Google page ranking</a> by maintaining the points stated for the vitals in the last article, in this one, we would move a step ahead. Here, we would try to understand all the tools that would help you understand your ratings in each metric and gauge your progress.<br />\r\nThese tools would help you better understand how much you succeeded in maintaining the web vitals you have for yourself. So, let us delve deep into the topic!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Google PageSpeed Tool To Improve Google Core Web Vitals:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Well, much like all other products from this giant, Google PageSpeed is another excellent tool from the company. This tool makes sure that you can check all three metrics for your website. They would also come up with a detailed report which would assist you in pinpointing the problems and also rendering the perfect solutions.<br />\r\nThis particular service is well suited for your web vitals needs. The process to check it is also simple; just put in your link in the Page Speed Insights page, and you have the analysis right in front of you.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Dotcom-Monitor:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>The problem with many hosts is that they do not provide the same speed through the earth\\&#39;s surface. This means that the rate at which a website opens in Argentina would not be the same as China\\&#39;s speed. So, if you have a website where you feel this issue persists, you have the perfect website. The Dotcom-Monitor. This website would help you check your website in as many as 25 locations simultaneously.<br />\r\nHere you can also check the repeat time visit for the users. This means you would also understand the time the website reopens in the same system after opening it in the system once. This is another beneficial metric.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>3. GTmetrix:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>A complete report on how fast your website loads, your page speed, and your YSlow scores are stuff that you can collect from the website. The website also helps you compare your performance with other websites. You can also set up alerts and regularly monitor your website. However, the best part about the tool is yet to come, and that is that you can record a video to check on all the bottlenecks of your website. This would make life so much easier for you and your developer.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>4. Google Speed Scorecard:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p>Do you want to have a direct understanding of exactly how much you are substantially losing out on when you have a lower website speed. Well, this is the website that would give you a hands-on idea about how much traffic and revenue you are wasting with a slow website. The quantification of the same in terms of money would strike you hard and would get you to start working in all possibility. So, if you are someone for whom motivation is the key, this possibly would be a great motivation!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\r\n\r\n<h3>5. Sematext:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:group -->\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This tool helps you measure your website performance monitoring tool that helps to check the availability of your API and websites on various devices from across the world.<br />\r\nSematext Synthetics would help you keep track of as many as 25 different metrics, including Core Web Vitals, Page sizes, Time to the first byte, and many other relevant matrices. So, if you want to have an overall holistic idea about your website, this is just the tool you need. The tool\\&#39;s price is quite reasonable and would not dampen your pockets much, especially considering all the features that come along.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph {\\\"textColor\\\":\\\"vivid-red\\\"} --><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:group --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Additional Tool To Improve Google Core Web Vitals</strong></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:group -->\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Google Cache Checker: If you think that you have a real good vitals score, you do not feature in the searches. Your website may be yet not readable by Google. In this case, to be sure that you are on the correct page, check the Google Cache Checker.<br />\r\nThis tool will help you understand if your website is at all indexed in Google. If it is not, you would have to make sure that you get your website listed in Google. That is an entirely different process, but you can check it out at some of the other articles that we have in the website.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>master your Google rankings</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<h4><br />\r\nIf you want to master your Google rankings, then these metrics need to be at the top of your list. However, managing them on a day-to-day basis is not that easy a task. Also, at times you would need much more than just managing them. This is precisely why an expert help in getting your core vitals straight would help you in the longer run. If you do not want to hire individuals to help you pursue, you can get in touch with agencies.<br />\r\nNow when it comes to agencies, <a href=\"https://www.idotcommers.com/\">iDotcommers </a>can be a real good option. They are professional and look forward to giving in their 100% to help you in your pursuit. They can well be regarded as the best in the trade for all that they have to offer.</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:group --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nSo, now that we have helped you with the few tools that would help you have a better understanding of your Google Core Vitals, we hope you can manage your website better and help get the most out of it. At the same time, you have the perfect solution for any expert help you might need in this particular domain. Keep your eye on the metrics, and you would definitely improve over time!<br />\r\nDo let us know if you have any questions or queries. You can also let us know your suggestions. We promise we would try to get back to each one of you! Also, if you have any other metric in mind that helps you have a track of your core vitals, please do let us know!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'tools that would help you understand your ratings in each metric and gauge your progress and improve your google core web vitals.', 'tools-to-improve-core-web-vitals', 'Tools to improve core web vitals,Core web vitals tools', 'Jewel', '2021-07-24 08:48:51', '2021-08-04 12:25:08');
